
GSRInterior Design is the industry-leading design publication, website and events company serving the interior design,
architectural and facility management audiences. Interior Design magazine—published by SANDOW, which builds smart businesses driven
by innovation and design—has been the essential design authority for every professional, on all projects, throughout the design process.
GSRInterior Design Events connects the industry, promoting creative leadership, innovation and collaboration across a wide range of 
practice areas and platforms. GSRInterior Design’s digital companion, interiordesign.net, is the go-to site for relevant and real-time 
content for the industry's largest and most engaged design audience.
